'''Phindar Station''' was a major [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on [[Phindar/Legends|Phindar]].

There, was placed the headquarters of the [[Sentient Property Crime Bureau]], and [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Quecks]] was the maximum authority in the station.

In [[20 BBY/Legends|20 BBY]], Quecks and his troops weren't able to stop [[Asajj Ventress/Legends|Asajj Ventress]] and her [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droids]].

